# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Frontend Environment Variables (Vite)
# Copy to .env.development or .env.production and configure
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Development ───
# These are the defaults in vite.config.js:
# - Vite proxy: /api → http://localhost:5000
# - Frontend: http://localhost:5173
# No environment file needed for dev (uses defaults)

# ─── Production ───
# Set VITE_API_URL to the backend API base URL
# Examples:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com/api
#   VITE_API_URL=https://backend.railway.app/api
#   VITE_API_URL=/api (if frontend and backend on same domain)
VITE_API_URL=/api
